Articles.Content:
Hey Guys. I stream a little here and there of my missions. I have only a few up from previous posts, and I tend too get on randomly, but please stop by, criticize(though politely <3) my work, and remember I'm not amazing at the game! Just a random Jessie going on her little trip through kerbal space. The videos are a bit short atm, I do plan on doing longer segments.

http://www.twitch.tv/ladyathena
Short isn't a bad thing, especially for raw gameplay footage. Your 2nd rover video appears to be mislabeled, though.
